data.description: Really adorable home! It's a 3 bedroom/2 bath home on a corner lot that was the model home when the community was built. It has so many great features including built in speakers throughout, water softener in bathroom, double reverse osmosis water filtration system, vinyl plank flooring, open living area. The yard is landscaped with fruit and flowering trees and more, come visit to see! Convenient to Randolph, Fort Sam and Sammc.
